{"tid":921035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度醫生疑醉酒接生被捕　母女喪命","createTime":"2018-11-29T09:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T09:48:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94cab23796a855086d16611dd542c9a826254ced","tid":921035,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"印度一名公立醫院醫生，疑在酒醉下主刀剖腹產子手術，母女雙雙喪命，醫生已被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的醫生拉哈尼（PJ Lakhani），在位於古吉拉特邦小鎮博塔德（Botad）的公立醫院服務15年。拉哈尼疑在酒醉下主刀剖腹產子手術，術後手術室外家屬被告知女嬰夭折，22歲產婦亦大量出血。雖然家屬立時決定將產婦轉往私家醫院救治，惟該名產婦轉院中途死亡。<br />\n<br />\n家屬指控拉哈尼醫療疏忽；警方表示，拉哈尼當時因害怕被產婦家屬襲擊，主動求助警方。警員到場後，發現拉哈尼酒醉，違反禁酒令，將他拘捕。至於拉哈尼有否醫療疏忽，警方透露現時正在驗屍，待相關委員會審查法醫報告後再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n（India Today／自由時報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181129/s00005/1543451483693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181129%2Fs00005%2F1543451483693&d=oW2ZKT0grFf0NVj5EkmC2LZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=3fa3aa83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181129%2Fs00005%2F1543451483693&h=5a68c925\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181129/s00005/1543451483693</a>"},{"pid":"11a4c01fc3a0be608c1283309296e6273c3b3a34","tid":921035,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"死得好<br />\n<br />\n印度做女人咁撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c689fe3c01e9b53392f37bc2c57fe5dcb3e468be","tid":921035,"uid":120117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">拉哈尼當時因害怕被產婦家屬襲擊</span><br />\n醒目呀, 出到去實俾人打撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dff3038727ef36c1ab4c70b39739841dd9aa72d","tid":921035,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-2